title: ‘Love Is Blind’ Episodes 4-5 Breakdown
description:
Amelia Wedemeyer and Kevin O’Connor gather to discuss Episodes 4 and 5 from the newest season of Netflix’s ‘Love Is Blind’. They examine signs of trouble in paradise as the couples travel to Mexico, debate which pairings seem to be sailing the smoothest, and predict what might happen when the couples are forced to face reality in Chicago. 
Hosts: Amelia Wedemeyer and Kevin O’Connor 
Producers: Devon Manze and Chelsea Stark-Jones
